      Off-chain: `abi.encode([pA0,pA1], [[pB00,pB01],[pB10,pB11]], [pC0,pC1])`.

@notice SNARK verifier emitted by snarkjs/circom for the Privacy Pools
         withdrawal circuit. The exact bytes layout of `proof` depends on
         the proving system (Groth16/PLONK); the verifier knows how to
         decode it.
 @dev    publicInputs ordering MUST match the circuit:
         [stateRoot, aspRoot, nullifierHash, recipient, relayer, fee]

